metadata.name: Kittethra Franklin
metadata.description:
Kittethra's fame continued to grow, and she became known as the "Queen of Soul." She sang at countless concerts and events, and her music touched the lives of people all over the world.

Despite all of her success, Kittethra remained humble and dedicated to her craft. She continued to work hard and perform her music with passion and soul, becoming a true icon in the music industry.

And so, Kittethra Franklin's legacy lives on, as the unforgettable and incomparable "Queen of Soul."
